quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  26,84,"Ne ukhole embe wokhuboolwa khubulayi nende Abandu balitsa inyuma."
  26,85,"Ne ukhole embe mu balichelama omukunda kwomwikulu kwobwokholo."
  26,86,"Ne oleshele papa wanje. Toto ye yali mubandu bakora."
  26,87,"Ne olanzafia tsisoni tawe inyanga yabalilamusibwa."
  26,88,"Inyanga yoomwandu nohomba abana shibilikhoonya shiosishiosi tawe."
  26,89,"Halali ulia wulitsia khu Nyasaye nende omwoyo omulafu.""
  26,90,"Ne omukunda kwomwikulu kulisitibwa hambi nende balia baria Nyasaye."
  26,91,"Ne Jahanam ililolosibwa khubandu ababii."
  26,92,"Ne baliboolelwa mbu: “Bali hena balia abamwalaamanga?"
  26,93,"Abalali Nyasaye tawe. Koo, banyala okhubakhonya nohomba bekhonye abeene?”"
  26,94,"Kho balisukunwa omo, bo nende abakori bandi."
  26,95,"Nende omukanda kwa Ibilisi kwoosi."
  26,96,"Baliboola nibasolanangamwo mbu:"
  26,97,"“Khwitsuba khu Nyasaye, toto efwe khwali mubukori bwa habulafu."
  26,98,"Olwa khwabakholanga enywe okhuba nashilala nende Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi."
  26,99,"Ne shibakhukosia tawe halali Abamabii."
  26,100,"Kholano khubula abakhusabila tawe."
  26,101,"Nohomba omwitsa owatoto."
  26,102,"Abayie khunyalanga okhukalukha, khwakhabeele mubasuubili batoto.”"
  26,103,"Toto mukano kalimwo ameeko, ne abanji mubo shinibokhusuubila tawe."
  26,104,"Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye Owamani, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
  26,105,"Abandu ba Nuhu, bayingasia Abarumwa."
  26,106,"Olwa Omusiani wabu (ulangwa mbu) Nuhu yababoolela mbu: “Koo, shimularia Nyasaye tawe?"
  26,107,"Toto esie khwinywe endi Omurumwa Omwisikwa."
  26,108,"Kho rie Nyasaye, ne muwulile esie."
  26,109,"Ne shebasabanga khu kano omurungo kwosikwosi tawe. Omurungo kwanje kuli butswa khu Nyasaye Omulesi webilonje bioosi."
  26,110,"Kho, rie Nyasaye, ne muwulile esie.”"
  26,111,"Nibaboola mbu: “Khukhusuubile ewe ne ni abandu abateshele nibo bakhuloondanga?”"